{
  "stem": "23090.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And I made it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "I made it through the first phase of the inspection.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "It was-- how I made it, I have absolutely no idea.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "I think they were preoccupied.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And those last transports or those last days, I'm not-- I'm hoping-- possibly second guessing, although I was part of this siege at that time, it seems like there was a lot of trains that are coming.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "Just was a lot of people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "I don't know if that was a normal thing, but it was just a lot of transporting, and a lot of inspection.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And that first phase of the inspection, they only took out young people, infants-- I mean, old people-- infants, people that could not walk, people that showed visibly defects, and were handicapped visibly.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "So, so the other ones-- and maybe they knew that they were going to get you on the next phase, because the next phase was in the, in the showers.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that first inspection was, basically, not as, not as stringent as it would continue.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I made the first inspection, and my dad made it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And some of my uncles made it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In fact, almost everyone made it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In terms-- other ones, that weren't-- small infants and children to the, to the fact.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And again, repeating, sick people and, and old people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the next phase we were in was-- I'm in this building.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was like a, like a sort of a warehouse building, and that's where they told us to remove our clothes.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, and there's another inspection.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, at that inspection, I, I-- again, to me as a child, I was not looking and thinking in terms, will I survive, won't I survive?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's just that you keep moving.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You just don't think about anything.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
